    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Vanishtan</strong> is a simple falling block puzzle game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >By rotating the falling blocks and connecting four or more of the same symbols, the connected identical symbols will be Vanish.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3251180/extras/df10abe5308192ebd4fac38e9a2a929e.avif?t=1771414638\" width=134 height=170 /></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3251180/extras/46238fd9641c420db45174152054a25b.avif?t=1771414638\" width=130 height=168 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A a bit unique about Vanishtan. when four or more connected symbols are Vanish, the other symbols next to them are Vanish in a chain reaction. For example, if four ice symbols are connected and Vanish, Adjacent fire symbols will be Vanish in a chain reaction.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3251180/extras/ebecd419cb464d20f3a4b79e69d276ce.avif?t=1771414638\" width=132 height=172 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Accidental chains that the player did not expect can occur, and the score bonus from the chains can be boost.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Of course, you are a skilled enough player, can be able to aim for a big chain on your own without relying on chance.</p>",
